,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"淨係睇wiki都唔係好明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T08:45:50.000Z","msg":"與這些年份相比，萬曆十五年（1587年）雖然有海瑞、戚繼光的去世，但終究只是無足輕重的一年，也即如其英文版的書名：無關緊要的1587年（1587, a Year of No Significance）。<br />\n<br />\n但黃仁宇提出與其他史學者不同的看法，指出此一年似是天下盛平，無重大動盪，實際上可能卻是明朝發展至盡頭而步向滅亡的一年。"},{"pid":"93502278f60afcbc6da39b99fd8d9d3fcdadcef9","tid":1568972,"uid":133866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a2aba12eee061d4f150e922fe55f3175dda94b3","tid":1568972,"uid":119135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"冇發生大事嘅一年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:57:29.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本人愚笨"},{"pid":"2e1eccd5a63d0542aa2f95db7fe58474411ffeae","tid":1568972,"uid":107686,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"93502278f60afcbc6da39b99fd8d9d3fcdadcef9","tid":1568972,"uid":133866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a2aba12eee061d4f150e922fe55f3175dda94b3","tid":1568972,"uid":119135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"冇發生大事嘅一年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:57:29.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本人愚笨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"萬曆十五年係一本好出名既書，作者認為此一年似是天下盛平，無重大動盪，實際上可能卻是明朝發展至盡頭而步向滅亡的一年"},{"pid":"b8b25eab32808b407b589fb6b50a9dcc57887ae2","tid":1568972,"uid":119135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:43:17.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊上任<br />\n死咗澳門中聯辦主任 郭氏兄弟其中一個<br />\n恒指創下33,484.08點歷史新高"},{"pid":"f0b21eac584377e22e09639d806434c373740189","tid":1568972,"uid":56533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:50:11.000Z","msg":"陳同佳單野就係發生係2018年<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113394ce27676971f522fd6ce9b1ebde552bd1e2","tid":1568972,"uid":290977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201